  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Telmisartan and Losartan in Primary Hypertension</brief_title>
  <official_title>12 Week, Multi-center, Randomized, Double-blind, Double Dummy, Parallel Group Trial Comparing the Efficacy and Safety of 40 &amp; 80 mg Telmisartan and 50 &amp; 100 mg Losartan in the Treatment of 150 Pairs of Primary Hypertension Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
