    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Boehringer Ingelheim</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Using Losartan as a comparator, to evaluate the efficacy and safety of telmisartan in the
      treatment of the mild to moderate primary hypertension patients in China
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
